    "description": "Are you a skilled Instructional Designer looking for your next big career move? Unacademy in Nagpur offers you the perfect platform to grow professionally and personally.\n\nAbout Unacademy:\nUnacademy is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Coordinate with academic counselors for student career guidance\n• Collaborate with faculty on curriculum development initiatives\n• Develop and deliver engaging lesson plans for students\n• Create curriculum-aligned learning materials and assessments\n• Support students with special educational needs\n• Participate in teacher training and professional development programs\n• Maintain classroom discipline and create a positive learning environment\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Communication Skills\n• Proficiency in LMS Platforms\n• Proficiency in Student Assessment\n• Proficiency in Classroom Management\n• Proficiency in Data Analysis\n• Proficiency in Lesson Planning\n• Proficiency in Child Psychology\n• Proficiency in E-learning\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Flexible working hours\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Learning & development budget\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Nagpur, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Unacademy!",
